message.body: Good morning, tigerlily...
It's angel.
Hey there good morning!!! How u doin?
How's your day. Mine so far is already behind. Rain causes the weirdest problems

Trying to get in the headspace to help a friend move furniture...in the rain. Everybody knows atleast one asshole with a truck.
I'm that asshole. :-)
Otherwise, i'm alright.
Rain does things usually reserved for mercury in retrograde and full moons.

Hahahahaha oh moving helper. I'm that asshole too. No truck, but I can't say no. Same problem. Wait. Is not mercury currently in retrograde and isn't it somewhere around the full moon? Well shit nice knowing you apparently I'm going to get murdered.@
Today's gonna be good, jules...for both of us. What's a hurdle when you're wearing a cape? Nothing, that's what.
Mercury is out of retro. Nice try. Can't avoid the day THAT easily!
Silly girl... Being murdered is so passe.
Hahahahaha ok fine. Hidden inside a tire well and tortured by tiny mechanics.
Lemme know if you ever need to borrow my truck. ;-p
I am wearing my cape today. Is it out of Ret??? Chuhh my gf who is my astrology go to is misinformed
Hahahahaha sure

Hey. Gotta jet. I'll check in with you a little later.
Have an incredible morning.
You're awesome.
Back at cha

Adding CEO of drenched rat asshole moving company to my resume.
You'll be CIO, supervisor of capes.
Hahahahaha
How's your day going?
Not awful! Over:)
Good morning, sunshine.
Morning!
How're you today?
I am okay. Dire need of Bloody Mary. Heading out to obtain such. Then I can be human. Ish. What're u up to
Errands. Drinking with friends later. Gap in the middle...
My day got all fucked up in a chaotic whirlwind of nonsense. how's you? please tell me you're having fun for both of us.
I have been sleeping since 2. Heaven. I know that whirlwind!!!! Tell it i say hi but not to come visit
I just woke up am all disoriented
Coffee tomorrow?
I just woke up from a 2hr nap.
I feel like my head is engulfed in cotton fog. The world is a scary place...
Yes it is.
Yes coffee!!! Afternoon? I hate having to get up at a time on Sunday !
Go back to sleep......tomorrow is fresh the fog may lift and there may even be a sunray
Dream happy dreams:) wake rested and well
Thanks. Yes, afternoon. Sweet dreams. ;-)

The day disappeared, as it sometimes does. But, i wanted you to know that i'm looking forward to us being visable, whenever that happens (hopefully soon).
Don't think for a second that you were forgotten. You weren't, and i couldn't.
Goodnight, jules...
No worries!! Rain check soon!
